import { Announcement } from '@mui/icons-material'
import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'

const Container = styled.div``

const ProductList = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Navbar />
            <Announcement />
        </Container>
    )
}

export default ProductList
